            <title>你还给傻逼织毛衣</title>
            <link>https://blognew.natt.cc/posts/2010-06-04-%E4%BD%A0%E8%BF%98%E7%BB%99%E5%82%BB%E9%80%BC%E7%BB%87%E6%AF%9B%E8%A1%A3/</link>
